Unsupervised learning
 The model is trained on unlabeled data.
 The algo tries to discover hidden patterns or structures within the data w/o any prior info or guidance.

 In this types of learning, the machince has to uncover and create the labels itself.

 Types:
  1.Clustering 
  2.Dimension reductionality 

  Clustering 
   Groups data into different clusters based on similar fts or distances btn the data point to better understand the attributes of a specific cluster.

   Ex:
 Customer segmentation
 Targeted marketing
